Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.43,0:01:16.68,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.35,0:01:18.22,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.06,0:01:27.94,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you ever even think that the guy might be you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.40,0:01:29.73,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Think that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.36,0:01:32.00,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.99,0:01:35.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,ME?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.62,0:01:44.42,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.63,0:01:47.42,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Still... even if it's just once...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.92,0:01:55.05,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I want him to think of me as a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.47,0:02:03.43,title,,0200,0000,0085,,{\fad(1800,0)\3c&H0A0909&\q2\pos(403,395)}Comeback Impossible! Major Heartbreak!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.89,0:02:03.37,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Just once...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.14,0:02:06.06,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,...I want him to think about me in that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.54,0:02:23.83,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,He's thinking hard. He's thinking hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.83,0:02:25.75,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,He's definitely realized this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.75,0:02:29.25,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, Risa. Your hard work has paid off!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.80,0:02:32.17,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I shouldn't have done that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.17,0:02:33.42,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I did something completely unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.63,0:02:34.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.51,0:02:36.22,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:38.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.18,0:02:42.14,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to do anything. You did everything you had to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.47,0:02:44.98,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's all down to Otani-kun's reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.98,0:02:45.98,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,His reaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.86,0:02:50.61,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better go tell him I was just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.61,0:02:52.69,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if he's an idiot! I like that idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.03,0:02:54.32,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Risa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.87,0:03:03.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nobu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.50,0:03:06.83,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I'll be in the way, but let me hang out with you on the class trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:10.29,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine by me, but what about Otani-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:12.46,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't spoken to him at all since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:13.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.99,0:03:16.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:18.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,And when we finally have our class trip too...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:21.26,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no! I don't care about the class trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.26,0:03:22.39,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.56,0:03:25.52,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I just remembered there's something I have to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.98,0:03:27.60,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.15,0:03:29.94,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Risa, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.40,0:03:34.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what do you think I should do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:38.20,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Go with whatever you think is best, just tell her what you're thinking now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:44.74,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm thinking now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:49.46,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted him to think about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.92,0:03:54.59,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,...but if I stop being All-Kyokin, then what will I become?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.42,0:03:57.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I really become a normal girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.61,0:04:14.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.36,0:04:18.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did you ever think that the guy might be you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.28,0:04:24.12,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,After going around in a big circle, I finally told Otani how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.04,0:04:25.79,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:27.16,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:28.54,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what is going to happen to me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.79,0:04:30.87,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so preoccupied with telling him how I feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.17,0:04:33.88,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I never even thought about what would come after.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:37.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's all down to Otani-kun's reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:38.26,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,His reaction...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.99,0:04:42.39,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, Koizumi, I've liked you all this time too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:43.39,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.64,0:04:45.85,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. That's absolutely impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.47,0:04:48.56,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared! I bet he's gonna say...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.77,0:04:49.73,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.94,0:04:51.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:53.69,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll definitely say something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.07,0:04:58.61,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, I'll just avoid being alone with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:01.11,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine as long as I don't speak to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.41,0:05:10.79,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? How long have I slept in?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.21,0:05:15.17,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Good morning. Koizumi speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.17,0:05:16.00,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,"Good morning"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.09,0:05:17.17,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You just woke up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:20.21,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You forgot we've got our class trip today, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.22,0:05:22.05,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been calling you for ages!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.22,0:05:24.55,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The bus to the airport is about to leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:30.56,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,L...Late!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.39,0:05:37.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,S- S- Sorry! I overslept!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:39.40,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't there anyone to wake you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:41.28,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone else at home was asleep as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:45.53,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking the two of you, don't pull a comedy act at a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.16,0:05:47.20,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,"The two of you"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.04,0:05:49.66,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.37,0:05:51.29,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm la...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.83,0:05:56.00,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Right let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.47,0:06:06.59,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I was planning on not being alone with Otani for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.39,0:06:10.26,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh. We're too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.35,0:06:14.81,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go take care of the tickets. You guys just wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.81,0:06:15.98,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Pair of idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:17.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.24,0:06:19.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Th- This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.61,0:06:22.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.28,0:06:24.36,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave us alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:30.53,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.58,0:06:33.66,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I said sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:41.96,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.05,0:06:44.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to act natural. Just like I was before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.13,0:06:48.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you sleep in on such an important day, you idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.39,0:06:49.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You did too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:51.22,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.41,0:06:56.02,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,W- W- W- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.15,0:06:58.06,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, to be blunt...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:06:59.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,NO!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:00.06,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't said anything yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.11,0:07:01.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No! Don't say anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.29,0:07:05.82,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been calling me an idiot for so long it's really starting to piss me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.82,0:07:06.69,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.07,0:07:09.62,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.50,0:07:16.54,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the guy you like really me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.42,0:07:21.59,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Asking so directly is bad for my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.59,0:07:23.34,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any other way to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.34,0:07:25.17,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,There should be!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:26.01,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't, That I know of.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.38,0:07:28.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, and answer me properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.73,0:07:41.06,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when I tried so hard to confess, you brushed me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:46.11,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have to make me relive that scene now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.57,0:07:49.36,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why... I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:51.24,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.37,0:07:53.83,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If saying sorry were enough, There'd be no need for cops in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:57.16,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to say it earlier, but you kept trickling away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.50,0:08:01.50,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean "trickling away"?! You make me sound like a shishiotoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.53,0:08:01.49,lovely - TL Note,,0000,0000,0000,,A shishiotoshi is a Japanese water feature constructed from bamboo, which clacks against a stone when emptied.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:04.55,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you realize that you haven't heard a thing I've said?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.59,0:08:05.42,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.55,0:08:07.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't you have said it in a way that's easier to understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.01,0:08:10.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I... like you, Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:12.31,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I said in very simple terms!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.32,0:08:14.06,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I came right out and told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.06,0:08:15.68,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.90,0:08:22.48,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.86,0:08:24.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.07,0:08:26.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.65,0:08:30.28,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're the one that wanted me to think in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.20,0:08:36.33,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:41.21,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,...but hearing you say that so seriously really scares me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.26,0:08:48.59,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here, All-Hanshin-Kyojin?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.01,0:08:52.18,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised. Are you regretting being late?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.72,0:08:53.34,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Y- Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.64,0:08:54.39,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:11.11,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The late couple have arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.86,0:09:12.78,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So they have.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:14.79,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Risa...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.91,0:09:17.79,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to you? I was worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.16,0:09:19.29,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.58,0:09:21.58,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they were together till morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.58,0:09:23.54,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:29.42,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Risa, I was worr-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.42,0:09:31.72,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take this! I wanna go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.68,0:09:42.73,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If you ask the seagull, "Have the herring come?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:46.11,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm just a migrating bird. Ask the waves."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.23,0:09:46.36,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,The plane trip was so long...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.07,0:09:49.36,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Otani sat right next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.36,0:09:50.82,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It was hard to breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.82,0:09:52.28,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think you're being overly self-conscious?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.74,0:09:53.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:55.53,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to think of a way to dump him five seconds before he dumps me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.62,0:09:55.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Dumps?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.45,0:09:57.87,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.87,0:09:59.95,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know if he's going to reject you, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.33,0:10:01.54,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I do know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.99,0:10:05.00,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get your hopes up about ever finding a boyfriend, amazon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:07.34,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't we All-Hanshin-Kyojin partners?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.88,0:10:11.17,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What? I... I don't get you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.97,0:10:17.43,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,To Otani, I'm just an amazon... and a comedy partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.06,0:10:22.52,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The thought that I might like him never even crossed his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:25.94,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I did confess, it'll never lead anywhere with someone who thinks like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.02,0:10:27.02,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:28.02,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Risa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.11,0:10:33.24,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But now that you've told him, you're not a part of All Hanshin-Kyojin anymore, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.91,0:10:38.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So at the very least, you've escaped from being his comedy partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.49,0:10:41.58,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great! You've worked hard and taken another step forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:47.08,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.63,0:10:52.59,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Nobu-chan, what'll happen to me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.97,0:10:57.09,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That depends on Otani-kun's  reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.47,0:11:02.81,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No!!! I wanna go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.81,0:11:04.18,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now. Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:05.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.23,0:11:06.44,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:08.06,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi-san sure is agitated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.69,0:11:09.40,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.15,0:11:11.73,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you slept so much that it made you late?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.73,0:11:12.82,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been getting enough sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.03,0:11:15.61,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that because you've been thinking about Koizumi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.49,0:11:18.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up. Don't make me hit you, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.87,0:11:23.32,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone this scary can't be Otani... sniff, sniff, sniff...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.33,0:11:24.58,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:33.63,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok, you're free to explore this area, but remember to meet back here at the right time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.89,0:11:34.71,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.26,0:11:38.38,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher the late couple isn't waking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.64,0:11:39.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake those idiots up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:42.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But they didn't even wake up when we stuffed snacks in their mouths.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:44.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with those two?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:48.39,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess there's not much we can do. Call them by cell phone and meet up with them later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:49.73,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:12:00.66,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi, I can't go out with a giant like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.41,0:12:05.87,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going out with this crab from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.87,0:12:08.79,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a Hokkaido specialty. She was just caught today, and is still fresh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.63,0:12:12.17,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Otani-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.17,0:12:12.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,A sheep!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:14.80,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh... Genghis khan sounds goods too...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.99,0:12:14.83,lovely - TL Note,,0000,0000,0000,,TL Note: Genghis Khan was the founder of the Mongol empire. This is a reference to the dish Mongolian Lamb.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.93,0:12:20.05,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.39,0:12:25.43,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.44,0:12:29.35,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.05,0:12:34.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.91,0:12:40.86,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.41,0:12:43.24,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Why has it turned out like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.33,0:12:46.45,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Glass? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.83,0:12:50.33,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you. We're at the Otaru Canal Craft Hall's-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:53.63,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Where? I have no idea what you're saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.21,0:12:59.55,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So we just follow the Otaru canal?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:02.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.14,0:13:03.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.31,0:13:06.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What did Nobu-chan say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.81,0:13:10.44,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,She said they'll get here soon, so we should run into them if we just wait around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.94,0:13:11.60,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, great.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:27.16,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This is so awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.25,0:13:31.75,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean I took a step forward? This is definitely a step backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.71,0:13:38.63,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If I knew it was going to be like this, I'd rather kept things the way they were, just saying whatever we felt like saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.30,0:13:44.22,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But now that awkward topic is all I can think of...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.47,0:13:47.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Did... Did I fail?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.31,0:13:51.31,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I shouldn't have told him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.02,0:13:58.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I really want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:14:01.11,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How awesome does that look?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.32,0:14:02.82,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.74,0:14:04.91,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a rickshaw!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:07.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How cool! It totally suits the atmosphere here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:08.83,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna ride it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.50,0:14:12.87,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.17,0:14:15.33,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be embarrassing and touristy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.46,0:14:16.63,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.25,0:14:19.46,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Let's go buy some souvenirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.76,0:14:23.67,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how they're doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.93,0:14:26.22,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope Risa and Otani are alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.43,0:14:27.55,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah. Found them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.23,0:14:40.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiharu-chan~!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.53,0:14:43.61,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuki-kun~!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.95,0:14:46.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Where should we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.49,0:14:47.62,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruka~!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.75,0:14:53.37,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.79,0:14:54.79,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:57.54,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you two doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.71,0:14:59.75,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The rickshaw was awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:01.96,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That felt great!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.21,0:15:04.01,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! It was super fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.01,0:15:06.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The driver even gave us nicknames.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.08,0:15:10.96,lovely - TL Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx99}In the long running Japanese TV Period drama "Mito Komon", Suke and Kaku are two retainers who serve Mito Komon (Tokugawa Mitsukuni).
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.09,0:15:09.39,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,He said {\i1}"How about I call you guys "Suke-san" and "Kaku-san"?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:11.01,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"You can bring Komon-san along next time."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.47,0:15:12.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a cold joke, but it was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.10,0:15:14.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna ride again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:15.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.73,0:15:19.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But we just did the 10 minute course. Should we go for the 30 minute course?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.19,0:15:21.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot. If we do that, we won't have any money for souvenirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:23.78,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we can just make some cash by doing a comedy act here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.78,0:15:24.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.86,0:15:27.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that things are finally going well between the two of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.33,0:15:32.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:42.46,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd forgotten all about that awkward feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.88,0:15:43.88,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.72,0:15:46.17,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go get some juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.47,0:15:48.18,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys decide where to go next.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.47,0:15:50.22,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.09,0:15:59.60,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I shouldn't have confessed after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.11,0:16:06.69,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It would've probably been better if I'd forgotten this crush and we'd just stayed a comedy duo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:11.41,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If I knew it would be this awkward...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.41,0:16:13.16,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'd rather things had stayed the way they were.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.08,0:16:18.12,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani-kun sure is slow. He still hasn't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.58,0:16:21.00,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he's deep in thought again...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.17,0:16:24.34,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.30,0:16:27.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Deep in thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:34.14,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, do you want to go shopping around here for a bit, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.93,0:16:38.35,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to do, Risa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:41.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go look for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.90,0:16:43.02,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Risa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:48.32,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If I hurry, I can still make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.86,0:16:52.74,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell him to just pretend that nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.96,0:17:02.04,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If we pretend that nothing happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:07.01,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,...then, just like before...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.06,0:17:22.06,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.32,0:17:28.28,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.03,0:17:33.74,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I found the bear curry that a friend asked me to get, so I was going to buy some.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.86,0:17:38.78,TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H2F31C0&\bord1\fs70\3c&H665D58&\frz270\pos(126,291)\clip(126,128,189,145)\t(0,778,\clip(126,128,189,275))\t(2154,3447,\clip(126,128,189,442))}Bear Curry!{\3c&H6C608A&}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.16,0:17:38.37,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Bear... curry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.87,0:17:41.75,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.46,0:17:43.29,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:50.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just pretend that nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:54.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I... like you, Otani!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:57.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did you ever even think that the guy might be you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.31,0:18:01.60,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If nothing had happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.98,0:18:04.81,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You asked me to think about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.86,0:18:07.61,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I've been thinking about it a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.98,0:18:09.78,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking about...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.86,0:18:17.12,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're asking me whether I like you or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.29,0:18:19.95,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'd say I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.08,0:18:28.25,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one I can make a big fuss and get excited about riding a rickshaw with.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.76,0:18:36.09,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But we've been a comedy duo for such a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.26,0:18:40.68,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I can suddenly see you as my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.31,0:18:42.21,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.04,0:19:00.83,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:02.66,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.40,0:19:11.21,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that serious expression?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.30,0:19:12.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's sickening.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:14.42,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sickening, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.59,0:19:16.55,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, it's fine. Forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.05,0:19:19.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just pretend that nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.56,0:19:20.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I actually came to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.22,0:19:25.06,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just stay All Hanshin-Kyojin from now on, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.06,0:19:27.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want, maybe we can join a comedy troop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.77,0:19:28.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.15,0:19:32.61,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, hurry up and buy your bear curry or seal curry or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.61,0:19:35.07,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, go on. Everyone is waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.28,0:19:38.07,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go catch up with the others, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.62,0:19:40.95,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Koizumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.43,0:19:59.72,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew from the start that it wouldn't go smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.85,0:20:07.02,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Even my confession was just to get him to see me as a girl for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.23,0:20:09.69,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.65,0:20:12.32,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.03,0:20:14.15,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Otani-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:16.15,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Otani?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.61,0:20:20.74,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, Otani is... bear curry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.50,0:20:27.08,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani is bear curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.08,0:20:28.21,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.79,0:20:29.58,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.75,0:20:30.44,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Bear...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.27,0:20:32.79,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Bear...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.21,0:20:34.00,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Bear curry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.13,0:20:36.88,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, what's this about bear curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.09,0:20:38.13,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.69,0:20:57.86,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, having it said to my face... it still hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.45,0:21:00.11,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Bear curry...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.11,0:21:01.74,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.76,0:21:09.09,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Bear...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.63,0:21:20.34,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I know about the bear! What happened with Otani-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.97,0:21:22.43,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Bear...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.43,0:21:25.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, what are you? The spokesperson for bear curry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.73,0:21:32.60,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason I feel like having bear curry now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.90,0:21:35.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Darling, please don't speak right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.49,0:21:41.78,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi Risa, heartbroken!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.89,0:23:23.34,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi, what do you want to do during our free time in Hakodate?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.34,0:23:24.88,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to get a soft serve!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.88,0:23:25.95,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Look over there! That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.95,0:23:28.31,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Umibozu, in person!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.39,0:23:30.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Lovely Complex~ Love Com.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.23,0:23:32.88,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Next: Back from the dead!! Aim for girlfriend status!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.88,0:23:33.94,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Be sure to watch!
